      "description": "Experience the magic of the season right on your wrist!\n\nFor issues installing or configuring the watchface, please see this tutorial: https://youtu.be/xEme-BFJWXM\n\nIndulge in the festive spirit with the \"Santa Christmas Snowing\" watch face, meticulously designed for Apple Watch running on Watch OS 10 or newer. Whether you're a fan of the jolly old Santa, his fleet-footed reindeer, or the quintessential Christmas charms, this watch face promises to deck your Apple Watch with holiday cheer!\n* Diverse Backgrounds: Choose from 15 enchanting backgrounds, each thoughtfully crafted with Santa, reindeer, or classic Christmas items.\n* Animated Snow: Revel in the winter wonder with a gentle snowfall animation, bringing a touch of white Christmas to your watch, irrespective of the weather outside.\n* Time Display: Adjust to your preference with both 12-hour and 24-hour formats available.\n* Vital Stats: Stay informed with the date, your daily step count, and the battery level, all seamlessly integrated into the design.\n* Easy Customization: Just a tap on the bottom left corner, and you can shuffle between the available backgrounds, right from your watch!\n* Personalization via Phone App: The companion phone app lets you swap background images, toggle the snow effect, switch between 12 or 24-hour time format and select your preferred color for the clock, date, and stats.\n\nSanta Christmas Snowing comes with a default watch face that can be installed from the phone app and a custom watch application created especially for you!\n\nFacing a hiccup? The phone app comes packed with a detailed FAQ section, answering common queries and offering solutions. If you still need assistance, our dedicated contact page within the app provides quick access to our support team.\n\nSanta Christmas Snowing also provides an widget for the iPhone with Christmas Countdown.\n\nWith the \"Santa Christmas Snowing\" watch face, not only will you be keeping time, but you'll also be spreading the joy of the season. Let every glance at your Apple Watch remind you of the wonders and delights of Christmas!",
